## 📦 Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|-----------|
| Frontend | Streamlit |
| API | FastAPI + Uvicorn |
| Database | SQLite / SQLAlchemy + Alembic |
| AI | Ollama + ChromaDB (RAG) |
| Auth | Streamlit Authenticator |
